        <abstract>
            <para>Records of  algae, chromists and some bryophytes, excluding INNS, from the Outer Hebrides recorded up to 31 December 2023. Includes records collected directly from individual recorders and those collected by the Highland Biological Recording Group (HBRG). Records of bryophytes collated after November 2014 are submitted to the NBN by the British Bryological Society. Collation and mobilisation of this dataset has been funded by grants from NatureScot.
OHBR maintains a regional database of records of the flora, fungi and fauna of the Outer Hebrides and the surrounding marine areas. Please refer to OHBR website (www.ohbr.org.uk).</para>
        </abstract>
